OL,3,CMan jailed for 30 years after setting
OL,4,Cfire to victim's house whilst she slept
OL,6,FA man who set fire to his ex-partner's
OL,7,Fhouse as she slept has been convicted
OL,8,Fof attempted murder and sentenced to
OL,9,F30 years in prison.
OL,11,FNicholas Martin, 63, was also
OL,12,Fconvicted of assault occasioning
OL,13,Factual bodily harm.
OL,15,FIn the early hours of October 22,
OL,16,F2024, Martin poured petrol through the
OL,17,Fletterbox of his ex-partner's house
OL,18,Fand set it alight before leaving the
OL,19,Farea.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/17
