OL,3,CMan jailed for 30 years after setting
OL,4,Cfire to victim's house whilst she slept
OL,6,FMartin had been in a relationship with
OL,7,Fthe woman since 2019. He became
OL,8,Fincreasingly controlling, monitoring
OL,9,Fher movements, preventing her from
OL,10,Fseeing family members and constantly
OL,11,Fcriticising her.
OL,13,FInvestigators at Salford Criminal
OL,14,FInvestigation Department found that
OL,15,FMartin had installed home cameras for
OL,16,Fmonitoring and controlled what she
OL,17,Fcould eat, wear, and watch on
OL,18,Ftelevision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
