OL,3,CMan jailed for 30 years after setting
OL,4,Cfire to victim's house whilst she slept
OL,6,FMartin was arrested on 23 October 2024
OL,7,Fat a hotel in the Lake District, where
OL,8,Fa can containing petrol was recovered
OL,9,Fin the hotel room wardrobe.
OL,11,FHe made no comment in his police
OL,12,Finterview and went on to plead not
OL,13,Fguilty at court. Despite later
OL,14,Fadmitting to causing the fire, he
OL,15,Fclaimed he had no intention to kill
OL,16,Fthe woman.
OL,18,FThe victim's pet cat was killed in the
OL,19,Ffire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
