OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read out
OL,7,Fin court, the victim said: "Martin's
OL,8,Fvile and monstrous actions have
OL,9,Futterly destroyed and decimated my
OL,10,Flife through his abuse of me during
OL,11,Four relationship, and the continuation
OL,12,Fand heinous escalation of his abuse of
OL,13,Fme after our relationship ended and he
OL,14,Fwas arrested, charged with domestic
OL,15,Fabuse offences and bailed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/17
