OL,3,CMan jailed for 30 years after setting
OL,4,Cfire to victim's house whilst she slept
OL,6,F"After contacting the police in
OL,7,FSeptember 2024, I was incredibly
OL,8,Frelieved when Martin was charged for
OL,9,Fassaulting me in 2021 and I was
OL,10,Finformed that his bail conditions
OL,11,Fmeant that he was not allowed to
OL,12,Fcontact me in any way. As we neared
OL,13,Fthe date of Martin's court hearing
OL,14,Fscheduled for October 2024, I was
OL,15,Fstarting to look towards my future.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
