OL,3,CMan jailed for 30 years after setting
OL,4,Cfire to victim's house whilst she slept
OL,6,F"I described in court my feelings of
OL,7,Fabsolute terror when I realised that
OL,8,Fmy home had been set alight by fire. I
OL,9,Fam still often consumed by the same
OL,10,Ffeelings of terror, experiencing
OL,11,Fflashbacks, distressing memories and
OL,12,Fnightmares of the fire and aftermath.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/17
