OL,3,CMan jailed for 30 years after setting
OL,4,Cfire to victim's house whilst she slept
OL,6,F"The worst part of the destruction of
OL,7,Fmy belongings is the loss of
OL,8,Firreplaceable items such as family
OL,9,Fphotos, and mementos of my late father
OL,10,Fand grandparents. After the murder
OL,11,Fattempt, I was left suffering extreme
OL,12,Ftrauma and pain whilst not being able
OL,13,Fto have any of my familiar belongings
OL,14,Faround me, and in the knowledge that
OL,15,Fmy home had been destroyed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
