OL,3,CMan jailed for 30 years after setting
OL,4,Cfire to victim's house whilst she slept
OL,6,F"It is impossible for me to
OL,7,Fcontemplate how I will ever feel
OL,8,Fstrong enough both physically and
OL,9,Femotionally to make a home and live
OL,10,Findependently ever again, and to
OL,11,Freplace and rebuild what Martin has
OL,12,Fdestroyed. My mum, son and daughter
OL,13,Fhave all also required trauma therapy
OL,14,Fsessions following Martin's actions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
