OL,3,CMan jailed for 30 years after setting
OL,4,Cfire to victim's house whilst she slept
OL,6,F"I will be forever grateful to
OL,7,Feveryone involved in the criminal case
OL,8,Fwho have worked so hard and so
OL,9,Ftirelessly to hold Martin to account
OL,10,Ffor his atrocious actions, and to the
OL,11,Fmany people who have shown me love and
OL,12,Fkindness through my ongoing
OL,13,Fpsychological and physical recovery.
OL,15,F"I do not know if or how I will ever
OL,16,Fbe able to rebuild some kind of life
OL,17,Ffor myself as Martin has destroyed so
OL,18,Fmuch."
