OL,6,FDetective Constable Zoe Bellis, of
OL,7,FSalford CID, said: "Firstly, I would
OL,8,Flike to thank the victim for having
OL,9,Fthe courage to report this ordeal to
OL,10,Fus.
OL,12,F"Martin undertook a campaign of abuse
OL,13,Fagainst his victim lasting a number of
OL,14,Fyears. His last act nearly resulted in
OL,15,Fa woman's death and I am thankful of
OL,16,Ftoday's sentencing result putting this
OL,17,Fdespicable individual behind bars and
OL,18,Faway from harming other victims.
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@AOU
