OL,3,CMan jailed for 30 years after setting
OL,4,Cfire to victim's house whilst she slept
OL,6,F"I want to express my heartfelt
OL,7,Fgratitude to the victim for her
OL,8,Funwavering support throughout the
OL,9,Finvestigation. Her strength has been
OL,10,Finstrumental in helping us build the
OL,11,Fstrongest possible case against her
OL,12,Fabuser and ensuring he is held
OL,13,Faccountable.
OL,15,F"I hope today's result marks the
OL,16,Fbeginning of her journey toward
OL,17,Fhealing, with the reassurance that
OL,18,Fjustice has been served for the
OL,19,Fmanipulative and appalling acts
OL,20,Fcommitted against her.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
