OL,6,F"Anybody who thinks they may have been
OL,7,Fa victim of domestic abuse can contact
OL,8,FGreater Manchester Police at any time.
OL,9,FWe will provide support, conduct
OL,10,Fthorough investigations, and take firm
OL,11,Faction against offenders. Your
OL,12,Fallegations will be taken seriously,
OL,13,Fand you will be treated with dignity
OL,14,Fand respect."
OL,16,F"Not all violence against women and
OL,17,Fgirls starts as physical abuse, and
OL,18,Finstances may go unreported as people
OL,19,Fin controlling relationships often do
OL,20,Fnot recognise the harm they face."
